data.description: Welcome to this spacious two-story residence that checks all the boxes for comfortable family living. With 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms and a versatile loft, this home offers the space and functionality your family desires. Downstairs you will find the Master bedroom with its beautiful full bathroom, and upstairs, you'll find three spacious bedrooms, which one is a mini master bedroom, each with ample closet space and easy access to bathrooms. The loft area can be customized to suit your needs, whether it's a playroom, home office or entertainment space. Located in a family- friendly neighborhood, this home is close to schools, shopping centers and I-10.
